Package datatypes

Class List<T>

java.lang.Object
datatypes.List<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type that this list is storing
public class List<T> extends Object
A custom generic list class we created to reduce code duplication, since a list is needed in most databases. Mimics java's ArrayList
